      <title>Class</title>
      <link href="/2023/05/10/class%20/"/>
      <url>/2023/05/10/class%20/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="class"><a href="#class" class="headerlink" title="class"></a>class</h1><h2 id="面向过程"><a href="#面向过程" class="headerlink" title="面向过程"></a>面向过程</h2><ul><li>将事物的发展划分为若干个块，以函数实现，最后将这些块进行调用和连接。</li><li>缺点：当客户需求不断增加，软件规模越来越大，开发周期长，难以维护。</li></ul><h2 id="面向对象"><a href="#面向对象" class="headerlink" title="面向对象"></a>面向对象</h2><p>20世纪80年底后期，人们提出了面向对象(Object Oriented Programming，OOP)的设计思路。面向对象的程序是由对象组成的，每个对象含有对用户公开的部分和私有的隐藏部分，将数据和处理数据的方法结合起来，形成类；再将类实例化，形成对象。面向对象不需要程序员考虑数据结构和函数功能，只关注对象。</p><h2 id="面向对象的基本特征"><a href="#面向对象的基本特征" class="headerlink" title="面向对象的基本特征"></a>面向对象的基本特征</h2><p>•封装性</p><p>把对象的全部属性和方法结合在一起，形成不可分割的整体，当与外部发生作用时，依靠接口实现</p><p>•继承性</p><p>特殊类可以拥有一般类的属性和方法，称为继承。被继承的类称为父类，继承的类称为子类</p><p>•多态性</p><p>父类的属性和方法被继承后，可以有不同的表现形式</p><h2 id="java如何定义类"><a href="#java如何定义类" class="headerlink" title="java如何定义类"></a>java如何定义类</h2><ul><li>类包含属性和方法（使用class关键字定义）</li></ul><pre class="line-numbers language-Java" data-language="Java"><code class="language-Java">class className &#123;    属性；    方法；  &#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ul><li>类可以分为类名和类体</li></ul><pre class="line-numbers language-Java" data-language="Java"><code class="language-Java">&#x2F;&#x2F; 定义了一个Person的类public class Person &#123;  int age; &#x2F;&#x2F; 全局变量  &#x2F;&#x2F; 定义了一个say的方法  public void say() &#123;    System.out.println(&quot;定义方法&quot;);  &#125;&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="java中变量的分类"><a href="#java中变量的分类" class="headerlink" title="java中变量的分类"></a>java中变量的分类</h2><ul><li>局部变量</li><li>成员变量（全局变量）</li><li>类变量</li><li>示例变量</li></ul><blockquote><p>类变量：用关键字static定义，调用时使用 <strong>类名.变量名</strong> 访问</p></blockquote><h2 id="eg"><a href="#eg" class="headerlink" title="eg :"></a>eg :</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-Java" data-language="Java"><code class="language-Java">public class one &#123;    static int age &#x3D; 18;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;        System.out.println(one.age);    &#125;&#125;&#x2F;&#x2F; 输出结果为： 18<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><blockquote><p>实例变量：与类的实例对应。当实例被创建时，分配内存空间；当实例销毁时，内存空间回收。</p></blockquote><h2 id="eg-1"><a href="#eg-1" class="headerlink" title="eg:"></a>eg:</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-Java" data-language="Java"><code class="language-Java">  public class Student &#123;    public static int amount &#x3D; 10;&#x2F;&#x2F;静态        public int age &#x3D; 24;&#x2F;&#x2F;实例&#125;public class Student &#123;    public static int a &#x3D; 20; &#x2F;&#x2F; 静态变量    &#x2F;&#x2F;public int age &#x3D; 22； &#x2F;&#x2F; 实例变量  &#x2F;&#x2F; 定义的一个方法    public void get_stu() &#123;        int a &#x3D; 18;        System.out.println(&quot;我现在的年龄为&quot; + a);    &#125; &#x2F;&#x2F; 主方法    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;        Student gn &#x3D; new Student();  &#x2F;&#x2F; 这里要new一个对象gn来接受值        gn.get_stu();    &#125;&#125;&#x2F;&#x2F; &gt;&gt; 我现在的年龄为18<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p><img src="https://flowus.cn/preview/1768feb8-7d0c-42f5-84e5-90c4064049ef" alt="image.png"></p><pre class="line-numbers language-Java" data-language="Java"><code class="language-Java">package com.pragect;public class two &#123;    private static int sid &#x3D; 0;    private String name;    int id;    two(String name) &#123;        id &#x3D; sid ++;        this.name &#x3D; &quot;hhh&quot;;    &#125;    public void inof() &#123;        System.out.println(&quot;My name is &quot; + name + &quot;, Num is :&quot; + id );    &#125;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;        two.sid &#x3D; 30;        two mm &#x3D; new two(&quot;mm&quot;);        two pp &#x3D; new two(&quot;pp&quot;);        mm.inof();        pp.inof();    &#125;&#125;&#x2F;&#x2F; &gt;&gt; My name is hhh, Num is :30&#x2F;&#x2F; &gt;&gt; My name is hhh, Num is :31<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="This关键字"><a href="#This关键字" class="headerlink" title="This关键字"></a>This关键字</h2><p>this关键字是java中的一个关键字，表示某个对象（不可以出现在类方法中）</p><pre class="line-numbers language-Java" data-language="Java"><code class="language-Java">package com.pragect;public class three &#123;        int leg, hand;        String name;       &#x2F;&#x2F; this关键字在类中的用法（我认为相当于C语言中的结构体）        three (String s) &#123;            this.name &#x3D; s;            this.init();        &#125;        public void init() &#123;            leg &#x3D; 2;            hand &#x3D; 2;            System.out.println(&quot;我的名字叫&quot; + name + &quot;, 我有&quot; + hand + &quot;只手, &quot; + leg + &quot;只脚&quot;);        &#125;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;        new three(&quot;Tom&quot;);    &#125;&#125; &#x2F;&#x2F; &gt;&gt; 我的名字叫Tom, 我有2只手, 2只脚package com.pragect;public class Student &#123;    static String words &#x3D; &quot; ##全局变量## &quot;;    public void getStu() &#123;        String words &#x3D; &quot; **局部变量** &quot;;        System.out.println(&quot;words的局部变量是&quot; + words);        System.out.println(&quot;访问的全局变量是&quot; + this.words);    &#125;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;        Student stu &#x3D; new Student();        stu.getStu();    &#125;&#125;&#x2F;&#x2F; &gt;&gt; words的局部变量是 **局部变量** &#x2F;&#x2F; &gt;&gt; 访问的全局变量是 ##全局变量## <span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="方法"><a href="#方法" class="headerlink" title="方法"></a>方法</h2><ul><li>成员方法（用<strong>方法声明</strong>和<strong>方法体</strong>两部分组成）</li></ul><pre class="line-numbers language-Java" data-language="Java"><code class="language-Java">[权限修饰符] &lt;方法返回值类型&gt; &lt;方法名&gt; (参数类型 参数1，参数类型 参数2……) &#123;    &lt;方法体&gt;    ..... &#125;eg:public void print(int a) &#123;  System.out.println(&quot;a的值为&quot; + a);&#125;&#x2F;**修饰符: public, private, protected, default返回值类型: int, double, boolean, void 方法名: 使用该方法的名字(一般定义为该方法的作用)参数列表: 传入的参数，必须定义参数的类型，有多个的话可用&quot;,&quot;隔开*&#x2F;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ul><li>类方法（只能对类变量进行操作）</li></ul><p>在使用成员变量或成员方法时，必须定义对象才能访问，而静态方法则不同，直接可以通过类名调用，前面+static修饰。静态方法不仅可以通过类名调用，也可以通过对象调用。</p><pre class="line-numbers language-Java" data-language="Java"><code class="language-Java">package com.pragect;public class Chinese &#123;    public static void say() &#123;        System.out.println(&quot;chinese中的静态方法&quot;);    &#125;    public void sing() &#123;        System.out.println(&quot;chinese中的非静态方法&quot;);    &#125;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;        Chinese.say();        Chinese c &#x3D; new Chinese();        c.sing();        c.say();    &#125;&#125;&#x2F;&#x2F; &gt;&gt; chinese中的静态方法&#x2F;&#x2F; &gt;&gt; chinese中的非静态方法&#x2F;&#x2F; &gt;&gt; chinese中的静态方法<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ul><li>实例方法</li></ul><pre class="line-numbers language-Java" data-language="Java"><code class="language-Java">class A&#123;    int a;    static int b;    void g(int x, int y)&#123;        a&#x3D;x;&#x2F;&#x2F;合法        b&#x3D;y;&#x2F;&#x2F;合法    &#125;    static void a(int x)&#123;         b&#x3D;23;&#x2F;&#x2F;合法         a&#x3D;x;&#x2F;&#x2F;非法    &#125;&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><blockquote><p>实例方法可以调用该类中的其他方法，但是类方法只能调用该类的类方法。</p></blockquote><ul><li>静态块</li></ul><pre class="line-numbers language-Java" data-language="Java"><code class="language-Java">package com.pragect;public class Test &#123;  &#x2F;&#x2F; static关键字修饰的静态块值纸执行一次    static &#123;            int age &#x3D; 32;        System.out.println(&quot;My age is &quot; + age);    &#125;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;        new Test();        new Test();        new Test();    &#125;&#125;&#x2F;&#x2F; &gt;&gt; My age is 32<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>不包含在任何方法体中的静态代码块，应用static关键字修饰。当类被加载，静态块就会被执行且只执行一次。</p><h2 id="方法重载"><a href="#方法重载" class="headerlink" title="方法重载"></a>方法重载</h2><blockquote><p>在同一个类中，出现了方法的名称相同，但是方法的参数不同。当出现调用方法时，需要根据具体的参数调用。</p></blockquote><pre class="line-numbers language-Java" data-language="Java"><code class="language-Java">package com.pragect;public class Calculate &#123;    final float PI &#x3D; 3.14159f; &#x2F;&#x2F; 定义一个用于表示圆周率的常量PI    &#x2F;&#x2F; 求圆形的面积    public float getArea(float r) &#123; &#x2F;&#x2F; 定义一个用于计算面积的方法getArea()        float area &#x3D; PI * r * r;        return area;    &#125;    &#x2F;&#x2F; 求矩形的面积    public float getArea(float l, float w) &#123; &#x2F;&#x2F; 重载getArea ()方法        float area &#x3D; l * w;        return area;    &#125;    &#x2F;&#x2F; 画任意形状的图形    public void draw(int num) &#123; &#x2F;&#x2F; 定义一个用于画图的方法draw()        System.out.println(&quot;画&quot; + num + &quot;个任意形状的图形&quot;);    &#125;    &#x2F;&#x2F; 画指定形状的图形    public void draw(String shape) &#123; &#x2F;&#x2F; 重载draw()方法        System.out.println(&quot;画一个&quot; + shape);    &#125;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;        Calculate calculate &#x3D; new Calculate(); &#x2F;&#x2F; 创建Calculate类的对象并为其分配内存        float l &#x3D; 20;        float w &#x3D; 30;        float areaRectangle &#x3D; calculate.getArea(l, w);        System.out.println(&quot;求长为&quot; + l + &quot; 宽为&quot; + w + &quot;的矩形的面积是：&quot; + areaRectangle);        float r &#x3D; 7;        float areaCirc &#x3D; calculate.getArea(r);        System.out.println(&quot;求半径为&quot; + r + &quot;的圆的面积是：&quot; + areaCirc);        int num &#x3D; 7;        calculate.draw(num);        calculate.draw(&quot;三角形&quot;);    &#125;&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ul><li>方法参数传递</li></ul><pre class="line-numbers language-Java" data-language="Java"><code class="language-Java">package com.pragect;public class Price &#123;    public static float GetPrice(float price, float heft) &#123;        float sum &#x3D; heft * price;        return sum;    &#125;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;        float price &#x3D; 3.5f;        float heft &#x3D; 6f;        float sum &#x3D; GetPrice(price, heft);        System.out.println(heft + &quot;kg的苹果要&quot; + sum + &quot;块钱！&quot;);    &#125;&#125;&#x2F;&#x2F; &gt;&gt; 6.0kg的苹果要21.0块钱！<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ul><li>引用类型参数传递</li></ul><pre class="line-numbers language-Java" data-language="Java"><code class="language-Java">package com.pragect;public class ObjectPass &#123;    int num;    public void change (ObjectPass ob) &#123;        ob.num &#x3D; 18;    &#125;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;        ObjectPass ob &#x3D; new ObjectPass();        ob.num &#x3D; 5;        ob.change(ob);        System.out.println(ob.num);    &#125;&#125;&#x2F;&#x2F; &gt;&gt; 18<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ul><li>构造方法</li></ul><blockquote><p>构造方法是一类特殊的方法，名字必须与所在的类名字完全相同。不需要返回值，也不需要使用void标识。用于对方法中未赋值的成员变量初始化，创建对象时立即被调用。</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://flowus.cn/preview/6975d44f-b329-43e2-8ee7-226e05dafb7e" alt="image.png"></p><pre class="line-numbers language-Java" data-language="Java"><code class="language-Java">package com.pragect;public class Fruit &#123;    public String color;    &#x2F;&#x2F; 构造方法    public Fruit() &#123;        color &#x3D; &quot;绿色&quot;;    &#125;    public void harvest() &#123;        String color &#x3D; &quot;红色&quot;;        System.out.println(&quot;水果是&quot; + color + &quot;的&quot;);        System.out.println(&quot;水果已经收获&quot;);        System.out.println(&quot;水果原来是&quot; + this.color + &quot;颜色的&quot;);   &#x2F;&#x2F; 这里的输出结果是绿色，说明在之前已经进行了构造    &#125;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;        Fruit f &#x3D; new Fruit();        f.harvest();    &#125;&#125;&#x2F;*&gt;&gt; 水果是红色的&gt;&gt; 水果已经收获&gt;&gt; 水果原来是绿色颜色的*&#x2F;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="对象的创建和使用"><a href="#对象的创建和使用" class="headerlink" title="对象的创建和使用"></a>对象的创建和使用</h2><ul><li>必须使用new关键字创建对象</li><li>使用对象.成员变量来引用成员变量</li><li>使用对象.方法来调用对象的方法</li><li>同一类的每个对象有不同的存储空间</li><li>同一类的每个对象共享该类的方法</li></ul><p>类名的首字母大写</p><p>变量名和方法名的首字母小写</p><h2 id="包"><a href="#包" class="headerlink" title="包"></a>包</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-Java" data-language="Java"><code class="language-Java">package语句作为Java源文件的第一条语句，为该源文件中声明的类指定包名。通过关键字package声明包语句。package语句的一般格式为：package 包名;    <span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ul><li><strong>import语句</strong></li></ul><p><strong>一个类可能需要另一个类声明的对象作为自己的成员或方法中的局部变量</strong>，如果这两个类在同一个包中，当然没有问题如果一个类想要使用的那个类和它不在一个包中，要使用<strong>import语句</strong>完成使命。引入的包，可以是系统自带的，也可以是自定义的。</p><ul><li><strong>public修饰符</strong></li></ul><p>•用public修饰的变量和方法称为“共有变量”和“共有方法”，当我们在任何一个类中创建一个对象后，该对象可以访问自己的public变量和类中的public方法，也可以通过继承的方式来操作成员变量和方法．</p><pre class="line-numbers language-Java" data-language="Java"><code class="language-Java">package com.d05.www;public class Example5_13_Tom &#123;    public float weight;    public float f(float a, float b)&#123;        return a+b;    &#125;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;    &#125;&#125; package com.d05.www;public class Example5_13_Jerry &#123;    void g()&#123;        Example5_13_Tom cat&#x3D;new Example5_13_Tom();        cat.weight&#x3D;23f;        float sum&#x3D;cat.f(3.0f, 4.0f);    &#125;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;    &#125;&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ul><li><strong>private修饰符</strong></li></ul><p>用关键字private修饰的变量或方法称为“私有变量”或“私有方法”，只在本类中起作用，在其他类中无法正常识别.</p><pre class="line-numbers language-Java" data-language="Java"><code class="language-Java">package com.pragect;public class Example5_12 &#123;    private int money;    private int getMoney() &#123;        return money;    &#125;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;        Example5_12 e &#x3D; new Example5_12();        e.money &#x3D; 3000;        int m &#x3D; e.getMoney();        System.out.println(&quot;money &#x3D; &quot; + m);    &#125;&#125;&#x2F;&#x2F; &gt;&gt; money &#x3D; 3000<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ul><li><strong>protected修饰符</strong></li></ul><p>们定义一个父类，其中有protected类型的变量或方法，此时我们又定义了一个子类，不管父类和子类是否在同一个包中，子类对象可以任意调用父类中的protected类型的内容。</p><pre class="line-numbers language-Java" data-language="Java"><code class="language-Java">&#x2F;&#x2F; 【例5-14】protected修饰符的使用．package com.d05.www;public class Example5_14 &#123;    protected int a;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;    &#125;&#125; package com.d05A.www;import com.d05.www.Example5_14;public class Example5_14_test extends Example5_14&#123;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;        Example5_14_test e&#x3D;new Example5_14_test();        e.a&#x3D;10;    &#125;&#125;&#x2F;&#x2F;【例5-15】protected类型变量的继承权限．package com.d05.www;public class Example5_15 &#123;    protected int a;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;    &#125;&#125; &amp;nbsp;package com.d05A.www;import com.d05.www.Example5_15;public class Example5_15_test extends Example5_15&#123;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;    &#125;&#125; &amp;nbsp;package com.d05.www;import com.d05A.www.Example5_15_test;public class Example5_15_A &#123;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;        &#x2F;&#x2F; TODO Auto-generated method stub        Example5_15_test test&#x3D;new Example5_15_test();        test.a&#x3D;10;    &#125;&#125; &#x2F;&#x2F;【例5-16】protected修饰符调用权限．package com.d05.www;public class Example5_16 &#123;    protected int a;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;    &#125;&#125; &amp;nbsp;package com.d05.www;public class Example5_16_A &#123;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;        Example5_16 e&#x3D;new Example5_16();        e.a&#x3D;10;    &#125;&#125; <span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><ul><li><strong>default修饰符</strong></li></ul><p>default类型称为友好的，也称为默认的，就是变量的数据类型前面什么修饰符都不添加．有以下特性。如果我们定义一个父类，其中有default类型的变量或方法，此时我们又定义了一个子类，则只有当父类和子类在同一个包中，子类对象才可以访问父类中的default变量。</p><pre class="line-numbers language-Java" data-language="Java"><code class="language-Java">&#x2F;&#x2F;【例5-17】default修饰符的使用．package com.d05.www;public class Example5_17 &#123;    int a;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;    &#125;&#125; &amp;nbsp;package com.d05.www;public class Example5_17_A extends Example5_17&#123;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;        Example5_17_A e&#x3D;new Example5_17_A();        e.a&#x3D;10;    &#125;&#125; &#x2F;&#x2F; 【例5-18】default修饰符调用权限．package com.d05.www;public class Example5_18 &#123;    int a;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;    &#125;&#125; &amp;nbsp;package com.d05.www;public class Example5_18_A &#123;    public static void main(String[] args) &#123;        Example5_18 e&#x3D;new Example5_18();        e.a&#x3D;10;    &#125;&#125; <span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
      
